### Decision 3 — CV value table

**Source:** pyarrow dump of reference `parameters`/`isolation_window`/`activation` + `OntologyMapping.cs`. [VERIFIED: pyarrow + file:line]

| Concept | mzPeak column / location | Form | Value(s) | Notes |
|---------|--------------------------|------|----------|-------|
